71-6318.Residential Lead-Based Paint Professions Practice Act; act, how cited.

Sections 71-6318 to 71-6331.01 shall be known and may be cited as the Residential Lead-Based Paint Professions Practice Act.

SourceLaws 1994, LB 1210, § 166;Laws 1995, LB 147, § 1;Laws 1999, LB 863, § 1;Laws 2007, LB463, § 1260.

Cross ReferencesLead-based paint removal, credentialing provisions, see sections 38-1,119 to 38-1,123.
